Audio Log 4732/1:  [Transcript of audio from an instance of SCP-4732-1 post-dialogue with Sinatra on 3/18/20██]

 

(Frank Sinatra and Dean Martin have just concluded a duet of the song  The audience is engaged in wild applause.)

